{
  "stem": "27335.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there, on the other side of the road, there was a corn-- cornfield.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from this side, I was crawling up, not very far, the elevated road, the-- the highway there, and looked around-- being on my belly-- looked left and right and saw absolutely-- absolutely nothing there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I stood up and crouched down to run across the road, all of a sudden, I heard 'Halt' from my-- from my right.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And about 20 paces away, a German Luger and a soldier behind it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Where it came from-- it came from, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Never--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then, after, I figured they-- they must have-- must have followed me already from-- from somewhere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They picked me up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, he took me back to his station, to border guard there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there he [INAUDIBLE] this and this, and back to the village the-- the nearest village.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They locked me up in a-- in a wood-- woodshed, and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then-- then he came back about two hours later with a car-- and back-- back-- back into [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From there, they put me in the-- in the--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The paper-- the paper that they asked me, it was a-- a-- a paper that belonged to a person who was from that area there, who was called into-- into the Hungarian Army.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But instead of going into [NON-ENGLISH], he just stepped over to the-- over to the Slovakia, to the partisans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there, when they [INAUDIBLE], they-- they took all the papers, then put-- and they gave it to-- to kinds of people like myself.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they looked at this paper, they just smiled.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
